<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>故事；传说；叙述：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>fairy / romantic tale</strong> 
童话/爱情故事</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>tell the <strong>tales of</strong> one’s experience 
讲述自己的经历</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Tales of</strong> the supernatural are common in all parts of Britain. 
英国各地都有超自然的传说。</p><footer>2008 广东</footer></div>

